
Q1) How can we see existing databases in MySQL ?
Ans -->  SHOW DATABASES;


Q2) How can we create a database in MySQL ? 
Ans --> CREATE DATABASE <name> 
        Ex->  CREATE DATABASE sports;
        
        
Q3) How to use a particular database in MySQL ?
Ans --> USE <database_name>
        Ex-> USE sports;
        
        
 Q4) How to find/confirm that you are using a particular database ?
 Ans --> SELECT DATABASE();
 
 
 Q5) How to delete/drop a database ?
 Ans --> DROP DATABASE <database_name>
         Ex-> DROP DATABASE sports;
         
         
 Q6) How to create a table in a database ?
 Ans --> CREATE TABLE <table_name>
         (
         here describe the column names and use appropriate data types for it
         );
         
         Ex-> CREATE TABLE cricket
              (
              name VARCHAR(35),
              age INT,
              nation VARCHAR(20)
              );
              
  Q7) How to see a table ? How to see a table is created properly and in the desired way ?
  Ans --> METHOD 1 : SHOW COLUMNS FROM <table_name>
          Ex-> SHOW COLUMNS FROM cricket;
          
          METHOD 2 : DESCRIBE <table_name>
          Ex-> DESCRIBE cricket;
          
          METHOD 3 : DESC <table_name>
          Ex-> DESC cricket;
          
          
 Q8) How to drop or delete a table in MySQL ?
 Ans -> DROP TABLE <table_name>
        Ex-> DROP TABLE cricket;
        
    
 Q9) How to use comments in MySQL ?
 Ans -> -- (i.e two dashes) are used to comment something in MySQL.
        Ex->    -- DESC cricket;      (It wont give any results as it is commented)
        
        
 Q10) What are some of the data types in MySQL ?
 Ans --> There are various data types in MySQL, a few of them are :-
         i) Numeric Type -->  i) INT   ii) SMALLINT  iii) MEDIUMINT   iv) TINYINT  v) BIGINT
                              vi) DECIMAL vii) DOUBLE  viii) FLOAT  ix) BIT 
                              
         ii) String Type --> i) CHAR  ii) VARCHAR   iii) BINARY  iv) VARBINARY  v) BLOB
                             vi) TEXT  vii) SMALLTEXT  viii) TINYTEXT  ix) MEDIUMTEXT  x) BIGTEXT
                             xi) TINYBLOB  xii) MEDIUMBLOB  xiii) LOMGBLOB  xiv) ENUM
                             
         iii) DATE AND TIME --> i) DATE  ii) TIMESTAMP  iii) DATETIME  iv) TIME   v) YEAR
         
